### Welcome to My GitHub Page.
    I am now learning Swift language, and have updated several projects I designed in my spare time until now. Though those projects is simple, it can be helpful to someone who is new to Swift. Because they are design with Swift 2.0 in Xcode 7 which is newer compared to those reference program online. I hoped these will help you in learning Swift.
